{"tid":1637960,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【佬訊專欄】請有效引用緊急法 - 佬訊","createTime":"2019-10-08T06:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T07:44:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fd43e17ef1e9cb58e7e98e9f118e1730578e213e","tid":1637960,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:57:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191007/LFFDK7XD4QQ7KEHGXWGFPCAX5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191007%2FLFFDK7XD4QQ7KEHGXWGFPCAX5E%2F&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIn4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=8c0cc33e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191007%2FLFFDK7XD4QQ7KEHGXWGFPCAX5E%2F&h=e07a89d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191007/LFFDK7XD4QQ7KEHGXWGFPCAX5E/</a><br />\n<br />\n【佬訊專欄】請有效引用緊急法 - 佬訊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/8vt7tDaKhIQc_ol_eH8rEgAwu6A=/190x126/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/OFLJK7GNVLR7U6SLMJ4DLJ4O6A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F8vt7tDaKhIQc_ol_eH8rEgAwu6A%3D%2F190x126%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FOFLJK7GNVLR7U6SLMJ4DLJ4O6A.jpg&h=8aece3f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n建制派立法會議員何君堯。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n專欄作家 : 佬訊<br />\n<br />\n耶穌造酒都尚且要水，林鄭卻可以在不進入緊急狀態下行《緊急法》，奇妙的邏輯直逼神蹟，果真是受上帝感召來打救香港的特首。<br />\n<br />\n可惜難得引用了《緊急法》，卻只立《禁蒙面法》，明顯是捉到鹿唔識脫角，既然都可以繞過立法會胡作非為了，為何不利用這個空窗期，好好整頓香港呢？以下是佬訊的一點建議，希望林女士能好好考慮下。<br />\n<br />\n首先，應順勢禁止反領polo。反領最大的問題，是反領polo其實也可以遮樣的，君不見不少阿叔下巴與後頸的肥肉，就像龐大的冰山一樣，埋藏在反領polo之下。當然，愛穿反領polo的大多是建制陣營，如何平衡持分者的意見，將是林鄭的一大考驗。但既然禁蒙面法都豁免了警方，禁反領豁免建制派想必也不是難事。<br />\n<br />\n然後，便應該禁止攝衫。近期示威者開始攝衫之後，精神面貌好了，前線的鬼少了，街上的混亂程度也減少了。作為與民為敵的政府，這是一定要禁的。教育局應再次寫信威脅學校，以後不准學生攝衫：「一般慣常、合理的着衫方法是不會攝衫的，所以同學在進行日常活動時，絕對沒有必要、亦沒有理由攝衫」。從此以後，香港學生當以衣衫襤褸、制服不整的防暴警為榜樣。<br />\n<br />\n最後，還可強制市民的衣着顏色必須根據社會地位來分類，最高級當然是防暴綠、速龍藍，然後是元朗白、福建紅、撐警藍，一直到在社會最底層的黑衣人。這樣警方執法自然更方便，相信林鄭一定心滿意足，畢竟終於能達成協助警方執法的夢想了。<br />\n<br />\n佬訊<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/loshunhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Floshunhk%2F&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIn4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=dc2a3e9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/loshunhk/</a>"},{"pid":"a20ac4915dfdb7b67696b0e0b9d8b428560bc75e","tid":1637960,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d528ff6d841dfee335b4bef6fb18d876fafd33e1","tid":1637960,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:44:26.000Z","msg":"請幫手推爆黑警散布謠言, 推到佢四點鐘又口啞啞!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［極醜惡又一例證］香港警察又掩埋真相 鼓吹謠言散播<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1636039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1636039</a>"}]}